---
import { MAILERLITE } from "../config";
---
<section id="email" class="section-shell scroll-mt-16">
  <div class="spotlight" aria-hidden="true"></div>
  <div class="relative mx-auto max-w-5xl overflow-hidden rounded-[2rem] border border-gold-600/45 bg-gradient-to-b from-navy-800 to-navy-900 shadow-[0_30px_120px_rgba(0,0,0,0.42)]">
    <div class="grid gap-0 lg:grid-cols-[0.95fr_1.05fr]">
      <div class="p-7 sm:p-10">
        <p class="eyebrow">Πρακτικές ενημερώσεις · δωρεάν</p>
        <h2 class="mt-4 section-title text-[clamp(1.8rem,4vw,3rem)]">
          Θες χρήσιμα εργαλεία και
          <span class="block text-gold-400">μια καθαρή εβδομαδιαία ροή;</span>
        </h2>
        <p class="mt-4 section-copy max-w-xl">
          Κάθε εβδομάδα: ένα εργαλείο, μια έννοια ή μια συνήθεια που μπορείς να εφαρμόσεις αμέσως στα οικονομικά σου.
        </p>

        <div class="mt-7 grid gap-3">
          <div class="metric-card p-4">
            <p class="text-sm font-semibold text-ink-100">Οδηγοί</p>
            <p class="mt-1 text-sm text-ink-300 leading-relaxed">Finance topics εξηγημένα απλά και καθαρά.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="metric-card p-4">
            <p class="text-sm font-semibold text-ink-100">AI εργαλεία</p>
            <p class="mt-1 text-sm text-ink-300 leading-relaxed">Νέα εργαλεία και freebies όταν αξίζουν πραγματικά.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="metric-card p-4">
            <p class="text-sm font-semibold text-ink-100">Πειθαρχία</p>
            <p class="mt-1 text-sm text-ink-300 leading-relaxed">Συνήθειες που χτίζουν οικονομικό χώρο, όχι θόρυβο.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="border-t border-navy-800/80 bg-navy-950/35 p-6 sm:p-8 lg:border-t-0 lg:border-l">
        <div class="email-embed-wrap">
          <div
            class="ml-embedded email-embed"
            data-form={MAILERLITE.newsletterFormId}
            data-cta="email-primary"
          ></div>
        </div>

        <p class="mt-5 flex flex-wrap items-center gap-x-3 gap-y-1 text-xs text-ink-500">
          <span>✓ Δωρεάν</span><span aria-hidden="true">·</span>
          <span>✓ Χωρίς κάρτα</span><span aria-hidden="true">·</span>
          <span>✓ Διαγραφή όποτε θες</span>
        </p>
        <p class="mt-2 text-xs text-ink-500">
          Μία πρακτική ενημέρωση κάθε εβδομάδα, με καθαρό κείμενο και μόνο ό,τι αξίζει να κρατήσεις.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .email-embed-wrap {
    border: 1px solid rgba(42, 68, 120, 0.9);
    border-radius: 28px;
    padding: 14px;
    background:
      linear-gradient(180deg, rgba(12, 26, 58, 0.96), rgba(15, 32, 68, 0.98));
    box-shadow:
      0 26px 70px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.34),
      inset 0 1px 0 rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.03);
  }

  /*
   * MailerLite injects a default white shell unless we override the whole tree.
   * The form itself stays unchanged, only the skin is restyled.
   */
  :global(.email-embed),
  :global(.email-embed *),
  :global(.email-embed .ml-form-embedContainer),
  :global(.email-embed .ml-form-embedBody),
  :global(.email-embed .ml-form-embedBodyDefault),
  :global(.email-embed .ml-form-embedBodyHorizontal),
  :global(.email-embed .ml-form-formContent),
  :global(.email-embed .ml-form-embedWrapper),
  :global(.email-embed form),
  :global(.email-embed [style*="background"]),
  :global(.email-embed [style*="background-color"]) {
    background: transparent !important;
    background-color: transparent !important;
    color: var(--color-ink-100) !important;
  }

  :global(.email-embed h1),
  :global(.email-embed h2),
  :global(.email-embed h3),
  :global(.email-embed h4),
  :global(.email-embed p),
  :global(.email-embed span),
  :global(.email-embed label),
  :global(.email-embed small),
  :global(.email-embed legend) {
    color: var(--color-ink-100) !important;
  }

  :global(.email-embed input[type="email"]),
  :global(.email-embed input[type="text"]),
  :global(.email-embed input[type="tel"]),
  :global(.email-embed select),
  :global(.email-embed textarea) {
    background: rgba(7, 16, 39, 0.95) !important;
    color: var(--color-ink-100) !important;
    border: 1px solid rgba(232, 200, 121, 0.25) !important;
    border-radius: 16px !important;
    box-shadow: inset 0 1px 0 rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.03) !important;
  }

  :global(.email-embed input::placeholder),
  :global(.email-embed textarea::placeholder) {
    color: rgba(201, 205, 214, 0.7) !important;
  }

  :global(.email-embed button),
  :global(.email-embed input[type="submit"]) {
    background: linear-gradient(180deg, #e8c879, #d4af57) !important;
    color: #0c1a3a !important;
    border: 0 !important;
    border-radius: 16px !important;
    font-weight: 800 !important;
    box-shadow: 0 16px 28px rgba(212, 175, 87, 0.24) !important;
  }

  :global(.email-embed a) {
    color: var(--color-gold-400) !important;
  }

  :global(.email-embed .ml-form-successBody),
  :global(.email-embed .ml-form-successBody h4) {
    background: transparent !important;
    color: var(--color-ink-100) !important;
  }
</style>
